Shougang, China Group to Develop Canada Coal Mines, Globe Says

-- B y   J a m e s   K r a u s
-- 
2011-03-31T05:48:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/shougang-china-group-to-develop-canada-coal-mines-globe-says.html
A group of Chinese companies led by
Shougang Group plan to spend C$1 billion to develop three
underground coal mines in northeastern British Columbia, the
Globe and Mail reported, citing Pat Bell, jobs minister for the
Canadian province.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
